{
  "name": "Spaded Sweetie",
  "note": "The Spaded Sweetie starts off with a 15 minute warm up to prime the engines and ready the mind.  Then, we move into a spade interval set starting off very hard, but short, and gradually reducing the intensity while upping the time... Only to go back up again!  From there, we will move into a progressive over/under sweet spot interval featuring changes in cadence and intensity that culminates in a 1min FULL GAS effort! This is a tough workout, but feautures a lot of quality time at VO2 and threshold. (by Shayne Gaffney | GC Coaching)",
